description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Yulenka purrs with a rating of 95, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 475, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Stringalong for East, Nine Lives for South, and Stringalong for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80955-77974-1.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [475 Votes, Hall of Fame]
